code: @Override public long extractTimestamp(KafkaEvent event, long previousElementTimestamp) {     // the inputs are assumed to be of format (message,timestamp)     this.currentTimestamp = event.getTimestamp().     return event.getTimestamp(). }
@Nullable @Override public Watermark getCurrentWatermark() {     return new Watermark(currentTimestamp == Long.MIN_VALUE ? Long.MIN_VALUE : currentTimestamp - 1). }
